{"id":2640,"date":"2025-05-13T15:57:37","date_gmt":"2025-05-13T08:57:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2640"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:21:19","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:21:19","slug":"cap-am-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/cap-am-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec? 3+ B\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy tr\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1c nhau, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe cho l\u00e0n da. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng gi\u1eefa vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y GSC s\u1ebd t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft da b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cap-am-la-gi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec? \u0110\u00f3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o da lu\u00f4n m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3824\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3824\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3824\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3824\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m th\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n h\u00fat \u1ea9m (humectants) nh\u01b0 Hyaluronic Acid, Sorbitol, Panthenol, Urea, Glycerin ho\u1eb7c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t Aloe Vera. Nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u00e9o n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c l\u1edbp da s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u00ec cho b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cap-am-la-gi-tai-sao-can-cap-am-cho-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u1ede tr\u00ean b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec. V\u1eady t\u1ea1i sao da c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m? C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu, mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng cho l\u00e0n da:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3825\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3825\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3825\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-2-3.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-2-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-2-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-2-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-2-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3825\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i: Ng\u0103n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng bong tr\u00f3c, n\u1ee9t n\u1ebb v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p thu: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o da, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m ch\u1eadm d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a: Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft gi\u00fap da \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nguy c\u01a1 g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da: C\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, gi\u00fap da ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f3 h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-diem-nao-da-can-cap-am\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o da c\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi da b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, k\u00e9m m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, d\u1ec5 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng bong tr\u00f3c nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb ng\u1ee9a r\u00e1t khi d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ea5t \u0111i v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng, tr\u1edf n\u00ean x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u00f3e m\u1eaft v\u00e0 kh\u00f3e mi\u1ec7ng. Nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c da m\u1ecfng manh d\u1ec5 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cap-am-va-duong-am-khac-gi-nhau\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m kh\u00e1c g\u00ec nhau?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m hay v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng hay c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1c g\u00ec nhau? C\u00f9ng xem ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><b>C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (hydration) l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh b\u1ed5 sung n\u01b0\u1edbc cho da, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da ng\u1eadm n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u0103ng m\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><b>D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (moisturization) l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n n\u01b0\u1edbc tho\u00e1t h\u01a1i kh\u1ecfi b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc trong da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Gi\u1ea3m c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng v\u00e0 bong tr\u00f3c da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu l\u00e0n da nhanh ch\u00f3ng khi b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Da kh\u00f4 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc trong da, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u1ea5t \u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; B\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu, gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n h\u00fat \u1ea9m nh\u01b0 gel, serum ho\u1eb7c kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u00fat n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a da \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; T\u1ea1o l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ed1c h\u01a1i, gi\u00fap da duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ch\u00ednh<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Ch\u1ea5t h\u00fat \u1ea9m: Hyaluronic Acid, Glycerin, Panthenol \u2014 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o da v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u00ec.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m nh\u1eb9: Aloe Vera, Beta-Glucan \u2013 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Ch\u1ea5t kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m: Ceramide, Squalane, d\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt (d\u1ea7u jojoba, d\u1ea7u b\u01a1) \u2013 gi\u00fap ng\u0103n n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ed1c h\u01a1i, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng: Vitamin E, Peptide \u2013 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u da.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; T\u1ee9c th\u00ec: L\u00e0n da tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng ngay sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n: N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m, n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bay h\u01a1i v\u00e0 da v\u1eabn kh\u00f4 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; L\u00e2u d\u00e0i: Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7: T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i cho l\u00e0n da y\u1ebfu, nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ai n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m?<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi da kh\u00f4, da thi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4 hanh, ng\u1ed3i m\u00e1y l\u1ea1nh nhi\u1ec1u.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi da kh\u00f4, da d\u1ec5 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng ai mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o h\u00f3a v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec ? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u00fap da t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, c\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m gi\u00fap kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m v\u00e0 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u2013 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m sau trong chu tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cap-am-la-gi-3-buoc-cap-am-hieu-qua-giup-da-luon-rang-ro\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec? 3+ B\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0n da \u0111\u1ee7 \u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, an to\u00e0n m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3826\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3826\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3826\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-3-3.webp\" alt=\"3+ B\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-3-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-3-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-3-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-3-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3826\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>3+ B\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-da-nhe-diu\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da nh\u1eb9 d\u1ecbu<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec &#8211; S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng, da m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH t\u1eeb 5.5 \u2013 6.5, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a sulfate, c\u1ed3n kh\u00f4 hay h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00ean c\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3828\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3828\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3828\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-5-3.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da nh\u1eb9 d\u1ecbu\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-5-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-5-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-5-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-5-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3828\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da nh\u1eb9 d\u1ecbu<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ceramide: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng \u1ea9m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glycerin, Panthenol: L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t hoa c\u00fac, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i: Gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t, v\u1ed7 nh\u1eb9 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ean da thay v\u00ec lau kh\u00f4 ngay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cap-am-cho-da-buoc-dem-quan-trong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da- b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m quan tr\u1ecdng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Toner kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn toner ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m s\u00e2u, nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hyaluronic Acid (HA): H\u00fat n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o da, gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Glycerin, Beta-Glucan: D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da y\u1ebfu.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t hoa h\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea1o: L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"uong-du-nuoc-moi-ngay-%e2%80%93-cap-am-tu-ben-trong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y &#8211; C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho da lu\u00f4n c\u0103ng m\u1ecdng v\u00e0 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i. N\u00ean u\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb 2 &#8211; 3 l\u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u1eefa ng\u00e0y khi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc. Ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ecdc, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3827\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3827\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3827\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3.webp\" alt=\"U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/11-4-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3827\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u01b0\u1edbc d\u1eeba: Gi\u00e0u kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t, gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3i cho da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e0 xanh: Gi\u00e0u EGCG &#8211; m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a m\u1ea1nh, gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e9p tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y (cam, d\u01b0a h\u1ea5u, l\u1ef1u): H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1ed5 sung vitamin gi\u00fap da s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf u\u1ed1ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e0 ph\u00ea, r\u01b0\u1ee3u bia v\u00ec ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m da m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"serum-duong-am-cap-nuoc-chuyen-sau\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Serum d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m- c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Serum l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong c\u00e1c l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng trong serum c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Hyaluronic Acid, Panthenol \u0111a tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00e2n t\u1eed: Gi\u1eef n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf c\u1ea3 t\u1ea7ng s\u00e2u v\u00e0 b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide (Vitamin B3): T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ceramide &amp; Peptide: Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3: Thoa serum ngay khi da c\u00f2n \u1ea9m nh\u1eb9 (sau toner). V\u1ed7 nh\u1eb9 thay v\u00ec xoa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00f3i chung, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p chi ti\u1ebft \u201cc\u1ea5p \u1ea9m l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u201d v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3 c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i. C\u00f9ng GSC duy tr\u00ec c\u00e1c th\u00f3i qu\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 da c\u1eafng b\u00f3ng m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y GSC s\u1ebd t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft da b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3829,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[12],"class_list":["post-2640","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong","tag-lam-dep-da"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2640","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2640"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2640\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3988,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2640\/revisions\/3988"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3829"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2640"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2640"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2640"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}